        <div class="body">
            <p>By adding the 'onsubmit' to the 'to-be-stripped attributes of the fieldset decorator, this can be avoided:</p>

<p>//In the form, add the following before rendering
if($fieldSetDecorator = $this-&gt;getDecorator('Fieldset')){
   $fieldSetDecorator-&gt;stripAttribs[] = 'onsubmit';
}</p>

